FBIS4-30211 "dreas122_n_94005" FBIS-EAS-94-122 Daily Report 23 Jun 1994 Vietnam President Sends PRC Condolences on Flooding President Sends PRC Condolences on Flooding BK2306152794 Hanoi VNA in English 1449 GMT 23 Jun 94 BK2306152794 Hanoi VNA English BFN [Text] Hanoi VNA June 23 -- Vietnamese President Le Duc Anh today extended his sympathy to Chinese President Jiang Zemin over human and material [words indistinct] on the recent floods to the people in the Provinces of Guangdong, Guangxi and Hunan. On this occasion, the Vietnam-China Friendship Association also sent a message of sympathy to the China-Vietnam Friendship Society.
